                        </div>
                        <h5 class="card-title">Request-Based Joining</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Players can request to join sessions, and admins can approve or reject requests to ensure quality participation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card feature-card h-100">
