                        </div>
                        <h5 class="card-title">Mobile Responsive</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Access your dashboard and manage sessions on any device with our fully responsive design.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card feature-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-clock fa-3x text-secondary"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="card-title">Real-Time Updates</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Get instant notifications about session updates, request approvals, and important announcements.</p>
